with ch rotation from 2 clerics and supplementary heals<br>
from a druid.  Had a 60 shammy use the poison based slow<br>
for which he died.  The group consisted of:<br>
<br>
56 rogue (me)<br>
59 cleric<br>
54 cleric<br>
60 druid<br>
56 ranger<br>
60 warr<br>
<br>
60 shammy ungrouped<br>
<br>
Just had the main tank keep aggro and we beat her down, <br>
the shammy slow helped quite a bit.  When i try her again<br>
i wanna try it without the slow to see if it's really necessary<br>
